profile.name: Vinay Kakkad
profile.bio:
I am pursuing bachelor's degree in Computer Science and Engineering at Ahmedabad University.

I have been making things for the web and have made projects that have been used by the community at my university. I am currently working as a backend developer intern at Flash Tech Company.

I am fascinated by the fields at the intersection of Mathematics and Computer Science and how they unite diverse phenomena by discovering secret analogies.

Personal Website: https://vinaykakkad.tech
